&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching an Arabic PDF used as a testcase.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Yigal&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12854066" author="lehmi" created="Tue, 6 Apr 2010 17:07:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;With version 931224 the converter isn&apos;t used if an unicode mapping is given.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;@Yigal: Please test that version, if possible. I guess it is easier for you to check the result, as I&apos;m not able to read arabic.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12854435" author="ydayan" created="Wed, 7 Apr 2010 11:51:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;version 931224 fixed this issue, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The other two issues I mentioned in the mail are still not fixed, so I&apos;ll go ahead and open bugs on them. Unfortunately I can&apos;t provide the fix, but I&apos;ll attach a pdf + results before fix and after fix, to make the problem stand out.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
